	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here's a little demo using $4011 to play raw 7bit PCM data while simultaneously doing some graphics stuff and reading from the controller.  This is my first demo so let me know what you think <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />   
<br />
<br /><a href="http://swiftlytilting.com/downloads/PCM.demo.wgraphics.zip" class="postlink">Download demo</a>

		

